Dee da da dee

29:25.388 --> 29:26.856
Dee doo doo
Doo doo doo da

29:26.923 --> 29:28.858
Don't step on a crack,

29:28.926 --> 29:32.421
or you'll fall
and break your back.

29:34.403 --> 29:36.703
[Growl]

29:36.774 --> 29:38.174
Heh heh.

29:38.243 --> 29:40.372
My stomach is talking.

29:40.447 --> 29:41.847
Mine, too.

29:41.916 --> 29:45.377
Hmm. l wonder what
this tastes like.

29:45.456 --> 29:46.685
Aah!

29:46.758 --> 29:48.989
The tree is talking.

29:49.063 --> 29:50.531
No, it isn't.

29:50.598 --> 29:53.296
You should not eat
talking trees.

29:53.370 --> 29:54.804
Nope, nope, nope.

29:54.872 --> 29:56.864
Brlrblblrb! Oooh!

29:56.942 --> 29:58.502
Aaooh!

29:58.579 --> 30:00.275
Hee hee.

30:00.348 --> 30:01.475
Aah!

30:01.551 --> 30:03.851
- Waah!
- Aah!

30:03.922 --> 30:04.912
Aah!

30:07.628 --> 30:09.563
Who are you? Huh?

30:09.631 --> 30:11.760
M... my name Petrie.

30:14.807 --> 30:16.207
Petrie, huh?

30:16.276 --> 30:17.904
Funny name.

30:17.979 --> 30:19.414
Uh, l.. l flied?

30:19.483 --> 30:20.541
No.

30:20.617 --> 30:22.052
You falled.

30:22.121 --> 30:23.589
l falled?

30:23.656 --> 30:24.919
Ohh!

30:24.992 --> 30:26.426
You cannot fly?

30:26.495 --> 30:29.466
How did you get up there?

30:29.533 --> 30:30.523
l climb.

30:30.602 --> 30:34.063
But you're a flier,
not a faller.

30:34.142 --> 30:36.134
Hard thing to fly.

30:39.384 --> 30:41.285
l guess it is.

30:41.354 --> 30:43.324
We can't do it.

30:43.391 --> 30:44.916
Nope, we cannot.

30:58.584 --> 31:00.109
[Gasp]

31:00.187 --> 31:01.348
Uhh!

31:05.797 --> 31:07.732
Aah!

31:35.148 --> 31:36.138
Uhh!

31:37.152 --> 31:38.141
Uhh!

31:55.350 --> 31:56.979
Aah!

32:07.439 --> 32:10.000
Mm hmm hmm
Hmm hmm

32:10.077 --> 32:11.545
Shh! Quiet.

32:11.613 --> 32:12.876
[Grrr]

32:12.948 --> 32:14.473
Stay low.

32:16.287 --> 32:17.915
[Grrr]

32:35.555 --> 32:36.682
Ow!

32:36.757 --> 32:37.816
Hey!

32:37.892 --> 32:38.881
Petrie!

32:38.960 --> 32:40.395
Get off!

32:40.464 --> 32:43.435
You got nice
flat head, Flathead.

32:43.502 --> 32:45.938
My name is not Flathead.

32:46.006 --> 32:48.202
My name is Littlefoot.

32:48.276 --> 32:49.768
Littlefoot? Hmm.

32:49.847 --> 32:53.809
Are you just going
to stay up there?

32:53.887 --> 32:54.980
Yes.

32:55.056 --> 32:56.456
Well, you can't.

32:56.525 --> 32:58.961
You're tearing my tree star.

32:59.029 --> 33:00.964
lt is very special.

33:01.032 --> 33:04.003
His mother gave it to him.

33:04.071 --> 33:05.472
She did.

33:05.541 --> 33:07.976
Ooh! Mother present
very important.

33:08.044 --> 33:09.479
l keep safes.

33:09.548 --> 33:11.540
Don't let nobodies touch.

33:12.653 --> 33:16.387
Yep, Petrie,
you keep it safe. Yep.

33:16.460 --> 33:17.428
Nope.

33:17.495 --> 33:20.398
l'm not a carrier.
Get off!

33:20.467 --> 33:22.903
You're a flier.
Start flying.

33:22.971 --> 33:25.567
B...b...b...but... waah!
Waah! Aah! Aah!

33:25.643 --> 33:27.737
Open your wings, Petrie!

33:27.813 --> 33:29.076
Open! Open!

33:29.149 --> 33:31.345
No can do this!

33:31.419 --> 33:32.751
You can fly!

33:32.822 --> 33:34.917
Open your skinny wings!

33:34.992 --> 33:38.431
Petrie, higher!
Higher like a flier!

33:38.499 --> 33:39.625
Danger!

33:39.701 --> 33:41.192
Where, Petrie?

33:41.270 --> 33:43.706
Th-th-there! Ahead!

33:43.775 --> 33:45.368
- Whoa!
- Whoa!

33:51.020 --> 33:53.513
Aah!

34:02.039 --> 34:03.302
Cera!

34:03.375 --> 34:04.901
lt's you!

34:04.979 --> 34:07.312
What happened?

34:07.383 --> 34:09.978
Why are you so frightened?

34:10.054 --> 34:11.214
Frightened?

34:11.289 --> 34:12.382
Me?

34:12.458 --> 34:14.985
Ha ha ha!

34:15.062 --> 34:17.396
Why are you
so frightened?

34:17.467 --> 34:18.900
We're not frightened...

34:18.969 --> 34:20.369
are we?

34:20.438 --> 34:21.929
Nope, nope.

34:22.009 --> 34:23.909
Well, you should be.

34:23.978 --> 34:27.917
l could be with
the other three-horns,

34:27.985 --> 34:31.424
but l came back to warn you.

34:31.492 --> 34:34.520
l met the sharptooth!

34:34.597 --> 34:36.293
Sharptooth!

34:36.367 --> 34:37.458
Ooh!

34:37.534 --> 34:38.935
Come on, Cera.

34:39.005 --> 34:40.438
Sharptooth is dead.

34:40.507 --> 34:43.967
He fell down into
the big underground.

34:44.047 --> 34:45.641
And that's...

34:45.717 --> 34:47.947
where he met me.

34:48.020 --> 34:49.112
Oh!

34:49.188 --> 34:51.056
Dear, brave Cera.

34:51.126 --> 34:52.594
Dear, brave Cera.

34:52.661 --> 34:54.790
Yes, l am brave.

34:54.866 --> 34:56.630
Sharptooth is dead!

34:56.703 --> 34:58.672
My father told me

34:58.739 --> 35:02.200
that flatheads had
very small brains.

35:04.817 --> 35:09.257
l was all alone
with him in the dark,

35:09.325 --> 35:11.989
just the sharptooth and me.

35:12.063 --> 35:14.659
l could hear him breathing.

35:14.735 --> 35:16.533
[Hrrahh]

35:16.604 --> 35:18.505
- [Hrraaahh]
- Aah!

35:18.575 --> 35:22.514
l could see
his one big ugly eye

35:22.582 --> 35:24.380
looking for me.

35:24.451 --> 35:25.544
[Gasp]

35:25.620 --> 35:27.054
[Hrrahh]

35:27.123 --> 35:29.024
What did you do?

35:29.093 --> 35:30.561
Huh? Huh?

35:30.629 --> 35:33.623
l walked right up to him.

35:33.701 --> 35:37.140
l looked him
straight in the eye

35:37.207 --> 35:39.574
and said...

35:39.645 --> 35:40.737
[Hrraah]

35:40.813 --> 35:42.213
Aah!

35:42.283 --> 35:44.252
Whoa!

35:45.255 --> 35:46.474
Uhh!

35:47.475 --> 35:49.172
[Snoring]

35:54.020 --> 35:55.853
Ducky!

35:58.027 --> 36:00.999
Hello.

36:01.066 --> 36:02.591
[Snoring]

36:05.340 --> 36:06.603
Hello?

36:13.588 --> 36:16.526
You should come out.
You should.

36:16.594 --> 36:18.028
You are late.

36:18.096 --> 36:19.564
Yes, you are.

36:19.632 --> 36:21.123
Yep, yep, yep.

36:23.104 --> 36:24.573
Come out!

36:24.641 --> 36:26.542
You are all alone.

36:26.611 --> 36:29.081
Are you not scared? Huh?

36:29.149 --> 36:31.051
[Yawn]

36:31.119 --> 36:34.056
We're going
to the Great Valley.

36:34.124 --> 36:37.061
You could go with us. Yes.

36:37.129 --> 36:39.599
Uh, you are a spiketail,

36:39.667 --> 36:42.695
so we will call you Spike.

37:13.894 --> 37:15.226
Ducky!

37:20.306 --> 37:22.172
So the five
hungry dinosaurs

37:22.242 --> 37:24.644
left for the Great Valley.

37:24.713 --> 37:28.152
There had never been
such a herd before.

37:28.219 --> 37:30.154
A long-neck, a three-horn,

37:30.222 --> 37:34.663
a bigmouth,
a flier, and a spiketail,

37:34.731 --> 37:38.670
All knowing that
if they lost their way,

37:38.738 --> 37:40.172
they would starve

37:40.240 --> 37:43.701
or find themselves
in sharptooth's shadow.

37:48.254 --> 37:50.190
Hmm. Tree stars grow

37:50.258 --> 37:52.693
where there's lots of water.

37:52.763 --> 37:55.529
lf we follow this water...

37:55.601 --> 37:57.194
[Sniff Sniff]

37:57.270 --> 37:59.706
Hmm. No green foods here,

37:59.775 --> 38:02.211
and l still hungry.

38:02.279 --> 38:04.749
l'm still hungry, too.

38:04.817 --> 38:05.875
Aah!

38:05.953 --> 38:07.888
[Sniff Sniff]

38:07.956 --> 38:09.892
Can you smell something?

38:09.960 --> 38:10.927
[Sniff Sniff]

38:10.994 --> 38:12.087
l...l...

38:12.163 --> 38:14.099
l smell... l smell...

38:14.167 --> 38:15.726
l smell...

38:15.803 --> 38:17.237
Hmm. Ducky.

38:17.305 --> 38:19.901
You smell me? Heh heh.

38:19.977 --> 38:21.411
l smell water.

38:21.479 --> 38:23.108
l smell...

38:25.319 --> 38:27.221
tree stars!

38:27.290 --> 38:28.724
Oh, look!

38:28.793 --> 38:30.227
Green food!

38:30.295 --> 38:31.923
The Great Valley!

38:31.998 --> 38:33.432
l found it!

38:33.500 --> 38:34.901
Cera, stop it!

38:34.970 --> 38:36.438
l found it!

38:36.506 --> 38:38.202
[Rumbling]

38:38.276 --> 38:39.437
Earthshake!

38:39.511 --> 38:42.950
We've got to get out of here!

38:43.018 --> 38:44.953
That way! Come on!

38:45.021 --> 38:45.954
Help!

38:46.023 --> 38:47.457
Spike, hurry up!

38:47.525 --> 38:51.328
Ducky, Spike,
get out of there!

38:51.399 --> 38:52.662
[Gasp]

39:02.752 --> 39:03.913
[Gasp]

39:06.058 --> 39:08.085
They're eating our food!

39:09.865 --> 39:12.267
Look, look what they're doing!

39:12.336 --> 39:13.804
They're so greedy!

39:13.872 --> 39:15.272
What about me?

39:15.341 --> 39:16.775
l'm still hungry!

39:16.843 --> 39:18.243
Haah! You hungry?

39:18.312 --> 39:20.782
l empty to the top.

39:20.850 --> 39:23.286
We at the Great Valley

39:23.355 --> 39:25.348
and still no foods.

39:25.425 --> 39:27.394
We be hungry forevers.

39:27.462 --> 39:28.521
Ohh!

39:28.597 --> 39:31.033
No, Petrie.
Cera was wrong.

39:31.102 --> 39:33.538
This isn't the Great Valley.

39:33.606 --> 39:37.170
Oh, it is not a great anything.

39:37.246 --> 39:38.680
Nope, nope, nope.

39:38.749 --> 39:40.718
We better go down

39:40.785 --> 39:43.187
and see if anything's left.

39:43.256 --> 39:46.695
Petrie, could you
fly up there and...

39:46.763 --> 39:47.696
No!

39:47.765 --> 39:50.201
Petrie, do not feel sad.

39:50.269 --> 39:52.705
Many things do not fly.

39:52.774 --> 39:55.540
Rocks, trees, sticks,

39:55.612 --> 39:57.308
Spike.

40:10.738 --> 40:11.706
Waah!

40:11.773 --> 40:13.537
- Hey!
- No!

40:13.610 --> 40:17.105
Ducky, push Petrie
towards the branches.

40:17.183 --> 40:18.446
Ohh!

40:20.489 --> 40:22.924
Ok, Spike, not too fast.

40:22.994 --> 40:23.926
Whoa!

40:23.995 --> 40:26.431
Ok. Hey, not too fast.

40:26.499 --> 40:28.435
Hey, not too fast!

40:28.503 --> 40:29.994
- Aah!
- Aah!

40:33.579 --> 40:35.070
Aah!

40:39.389 --> 40:41.859
You four look so ridiculous.

40:41.926 --> 40:45.091
Ha ha ha ha!

41:04.800 --> 41:06.531
Ohh!

41:06.603 --> 41:09.038
Ducky, Petrie,
come down here!

41:09.108 --> 41:11.077
We've got green food!

41:11.144 --> 41:13.080
Fly, Petrie!

41:13.148 --> 41:14.206
Aah!

41:14.283 --> 41:16.685
Fly, Petrie!
Flap your wings!

41:16.754 --> 41:18.245
[Awk]

41:25.837 --> 41:27.328
l flied?

41:28.876 --> 41:32.575
Come on, Cera.
We've got green food.

41:32.648 --> 41:36.451
l can get my own green food.

42:01.466 --> 42:05.405
See? l can take care of myself...

42:05.473 --> 42:07.443
all by myself.

42:09.881 --> 42:13.410
And l'm not afraid to be alone!

42:14.489 --> 42:17.358
l know my way to go,

42:17.427 --> 42:20.399
and l'm not
afraid of sharptooth!

42:20.466 --> 42:24.405
l hope he doesn't eat any of you.

42:24.473 --> 42:27.774
Don't worry.
There isn't any sharptooth.

42:27.846 --> 42:28.905
[Gasp]

42:28.981 --> 42:30.917
Sharptooth!

42:30.985 --> 42:32.214
Spike.

42:32.287 --> 42:33.846
Ahem.

43:04.510 --> 43:05.739
[Sigh]

43:05.812 --> 43:08.282
There isn't any sharptooth.

44:23.249 --> 44:24.683
Mmm.

44:24.751 --> 44:26.344
Mmm.

44:34.201 --> 44:35.499
[Thud]

44:46.022 --> 44:47.183
Ohh!

45:41.954 --> 45:43.946
[Grrr]

45:46.628 --> 45:47.721
[Grrr]

45:47.797 --> 45:49.732
Wake up.

45:49.800 --> 45:51.292
Wake up!

45:52.973 --> 45:55.033
Wake up!

45:55.110 --> 45:56.544
Hey, stop that.

45:56.613 --> 45:58.081
Shh! lt's sharptooth.

45:58.149 --> 45:59.549
Cera, stop it.

45:59.618 --> 46:01.781
Shh! He'll eat us.

46:01.855 --> 46:03.824
He'll eat us! Run!

46:03.892 --> 46:05.383
Come back!

46:12.641 --> 46:16.375
Don't look back!
Keep going!

46:22.091 --> 46:23.354
Aah!

46:31.674 --> 46:34.110
Now will you believe me?

46:34.178 --> 46:35.646
We're safe now.

46:35.714 --> 46:38.241
Nobody's safe with you.

46:40.156 --> 46:43.650
Look. That rock
looks like a long-neck,

46:43.728 --> 46:45.630
like my mother said.

46:45.699 --> 46:48.192
We're going the right way,

46:48.270 --> 46:51.241
the way to the Great Valley!

46:53.713 --> 46:56.650
Littlefoot had been wrong
about the sharptooth,

46:56.718 --> 46:58.654
but the others followed.

46:58.722 --> 47:02.160
Their only hope
was the Great Valley.

47:02.227 --> 47:04.754
Littlefoot alone knew the way.

47:15.785 --> 47:17.777
Come on. Get up.

47:17.855 --> 47:20.291
We're going the right way.

47:20.360 --> 47:22.421
We got to keep moving.

47:22.497 --> 47:23.931
You can't quit.

47:23.999 --> 47:26.469
What if the Great Valley

47:26.537 --> 47:29.030
is just over these rocks?

47:30.277 --> 47:33.214
Though they were
sore-stumped and tired,

47:33.282 --> 47:35.217
Littlefoot urged them on.

47:35.286 --> 47:38.257
He'd never seen
the Great Valley,

47:38.325 --> 47:42.230
but his heart told him
they were close.

47:42.298 --> 47:45.828
Surely at the top,
they'd behold it.

47:57.287 --> 47:59.723
This is your Great Valley?

47:59.792 --> 48:01.887
You're crazy.

48:01.963 --> 48:03.363
l'm leaving.

48:03.432 --> 48:07.394
Cera, we have to keep
following the bright circle.

48:07.472 --> 48:09.874
l'm taking the easy way.

48:09.943 --> 48:11.878
lt's the wrong way.

48:11.946 --> 48:13.414
Who says?

48:13.483 --> 48:14.917
My mother.

48:14.986 --> 48:17.387
Then she was stupid, too.

48:17.457 --> 48:18.925
Take that back.

48:18.993 --> 48:20.052
Never.

48:20.128 --> 48:21.562
Take it back!

48:21.631 --> 48:22.792
No!

48:26.205 --> 48:27.468
Spike!

48:27.541 --> 48:28.941
Spike, stop!

48:29.010 --> 48:31.139
Don't fall!

48:34.587 --> 48:35.815
You!

48:38.561 --> 48:41.259
Let go of my leg!

48:53.420 --> 48:54.581
Spike.

48:57.427 --> 48:59.020
Take that!

49:07.612 --> 49:09.046
Huh!

49:15.959 --> 49:17.359
Go on!

49:17.428 --> 49:19.364
Go the wrong way.

49:19.432 --> 49:22.961
We never wanted you
with us anyway.

49:24.675 --> 49:28.169
Come on.
We have to keep going.

49:32.521 --> 49:34.218
Come on.

49:37.831 --> 49:40.927
Cera's way is easier.

49:41.003 --> 49:43.769
l think so, too.

49:47.148 --> 49:49.413
Oh, Flathead, wait!

49:49.484 --> 49:52.422
Ooh! Aah! Ow!

49:52.490 --> 49:53.890
No be angry.

49:53.960 --> 49:57.193
Wait!

49:59.869 --> 50:01.771
Cera, wait for us!

50:01.840 --> 50:05.334
We're coming with you, Cera!

50:05.412 --> 50:08.509
Cera, Spike, wait!

50:24.580 --> 50:29.020
l wish Littlefoot
was here with us now.

50:29.087 --> 50:31.854
Me, too.

50:32.861 --> 50:34.022
Spike.

50:35.565 --> 50:37.535
Spike, do not stop.

50:37.603 --> 50:39.800
We must stay together.

50:58.773 --> 51:01.300
A... a... a... aah!

51:02.313 --> 51:04.407
Aah!

51:06.620 --> 51:08.054
Whoa! Cera, l...

51:08.123 --> 51:11.459
Whoa! Oh, Cera,
Ducky, Spike!

51:11.529 --> 51:13.896
Help!

51:13.966 --> 51:16.436
Help, Cera!

51:17.606 --> 51:19.633
Cera, where are you?

51:22.648 --> 51:23.775
Littlefoot!

51:23.851 --> 51:24.910
Ducky!

51:24.986 --> 51:26.079
Littlefoot!

51:26.155 --> 51:28.751
Hang on! l'm coming!

51:34.169 --> 51:36.035
Littlefoot!

51:40.714 --> 51:42.307
Quick, this way!

51:44.721 --> 51:46.622
Hang on, Petrie!

51:46.690 --> 51:48.717
Help!

51:51.065 --> 51:52.294
Ooh!

51:52.368 --> 51:53.961
Ducky! Spike!

51:54.037 --> 51:56.439
Oh, Petrie am so happy.

51:56.508 --> 51:58.306
Jump, Petrie!

52:00.080 --> 52:01.913
Help, Ducky!

52:05.023 --> 52:07.152
Petrie, pull!

52:09.565 --> 52:10.897
Petrie.

52:13.772 --> 52:14.831
Aah!

52:14.907 --> 52:16.136
Help!

52:16.210 --> 52:17.542
Help!

52:25.759 --> 52:27.159
Aah!

52:29.766 --> 52:31.667
Aah! Help me!

52:31.736 --> 52:32.829
Help!

52:34.642 --> 52:36.133
Woo!

52:45.694 --> 52:47.664
Get away from me!

52:47.732 --> 52:48.630
Aah!

52:48.699 --> 52:50.259
Let go of me!

52:50.336 --> 52:51.736
Help!

52:51.805 --> 52:53.273
Help!

52:53.341 --> 52:56.744
Petrie, Spike, Ducky, help!

52:56.814 --> 52:59.910
Cera, it is us.

53:11.172 --> 53:12.333
Aah!

53:13.510 --> 53:14.603
Ha ha ha!

53:14.679 --> 53:19.245
l knew it was you
all along. l did!

53:23.361 --> 53:26.389
Oh, get out of my way.

53:44.230 --> 53:45.357
Cera?

53:45.432 --> 53:47.095
Cera, come back!

53:47.169 --> 53:48.467
Come back!

53:48.538 --> 53:52.443
Cera was still too proud
to admit that...

53:52.512 --> 53:55.108
she'd gone the wrong way.

54:03.798 --> 54:05.791
[Crying]

54:31.013 --> 54:32.447
[Grrr]

54:32.515 --> 54:33.574
Aah!

54:33.651 --> 54:35.244
Sharptooth!

54:36.522 --> 54:38.424
lt's sharptooth.

54:40.997 --> 54:44.491
Let's get rid of him for good.

54:44.570 --> 54:47.701
We'll coax him to deep water.

54:47.776 --> 54:50.975
He can't swim
with scrawny arms.

54:51.048 --> 54:55.716
Me and Spike will push
that rock on his head.

54:55.790 --> 54:58.283
He'll fall into the water.

54:58.361 --> 55:02.824
Petrie, whistle when he's
where the water gets dark.

55:02.902 --> 55:05.338
Now we need some bait.

